      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"App Icon\" /\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eWelcome to the Company Locator By Sector!\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      This AI-powered application helps you list and rank companies by industry and geography. Using generative models and powered by live web search via Serper, the system extracts structured company data from the internet, enriches it, and ranks each lead by quality, relevance, and business value.\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eindustry\u003c/strong\u003e (required): The sector of companies you\u0027re interested in (e.g., \"Fintech\", \"Biotech\")\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003elocation\u003c/strong\u003e (required): The geographic region to search within (e.g., \"San Francisco\", \"India\")\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e A HTML table will get printed with the following fields\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompany Name\u003c/strong\u003e: Name of the company\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIndustry\u003c/strong\u003e: Same as the input industry\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLocation\u003c/strong\u003e: Same as the input location\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEstablished Year\u003c/strong\u003e: Year the company was founded\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNumber Of Employees\u003c/strong\u003e: Approximate team size\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSource Url\u003c/strong\u003e: Website or source used for data extraction\u003c/li\u003e\n        \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eScore\u003c/strong\u003e: Relevance and quality score from 0â€“100\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n",
